opta-xenm (1.1.0) stable; urgency=low
  
  * New minor version because I felt like it
  * Now remembers memory size on respawn
  * Add option to set memory size on command line when spawning and respawning
    (e.g. xenm spawn -m 512 myNewVm)

 -- Alex Forbes <alex.forbes@optasports.com>  Thu, 14 Feb 2013 19:29:00 +0000 

opta-xenm (1.0.6) stable; urgency=low

  * Sort output of xenm list by pool, replicant status, name
  * Reduce number of API calls in get_ methods (small performance improvement)
  * xenm status now lists attributes by line rather than column
  
